description:
This course explores an aspect of 19th-century literature intensively; specific course topics will vary from year to year. 

See the English Department's website at www.english.upenn.edu for a description of the current offerings.
name: VICTORIAN LITERATURE: Sympathetic Ink:  Empire and Material Text in Victorian Literature
